{"tid":1011463,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每人一段中學最遺憾的感情","createTime":"2019-02-06T19:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T01:49:12.000Z","uid":105396,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5c020531484b63f35554c0511e0df20a5cc43856","tid":1011463,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:32:39.000Z","msg":"以前中學有個女朋友對我好好<br />\n仲記得第一次出街食飯幾貴下，我諗住比錢埋單<br />\n佢捉住我隻手笑住同我講：你唔洗扮大方啦，我地仲係學生，分開比咪得，等你搵到錢先再請我啦傻佬。<br />\n我聽到之後真係眼濕濕，好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次其他人睇死我，話我廢柴，得佢一個留守係我身邊，支持我，開解我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陪我係中學個陣捱窮，明明大把男仔好條件過我，但係佢都依然對我忠一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜我對自己無自信，後來就同佢分左手。我真係好想返去過去打撚醒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家嘅我唔算好成功，但唔會窮，但係佢已經唔係我身邊，我真係好愛佢，好想比幸褔佢<br />\n每次聽到eason首天下無雙都諗起你，我真係好掛住你，除左我屋企人對我最好個個就係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好掛住你"},{"pid":"bf816c2dde1d9891e096020eb49ea3fa57a72bfc","tid":1011463,"uid":105396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"如果有得返去以前我一定會抱實你唔比你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff7ac8642ec3b1b25b02e8b951c17538756752c","tid":1011463,"uid":220799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"冇 因為從來都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da61f3a7edf574333383c5810d863e8aaefede33","tid":1011463,"uid":93905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:35:49.000Z","msg":"唔追返？佢呢家有冇變？"},{"pid":"92feb74e0d90c6a92a86e6046fc31a98d2f3d96e","tid":1011463,"uid":105396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da61f3a7edf574333383c5810d863e8aaefede33","tid":1011463,"uid":93905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T19:35:49.000Z","msg":"唔追返？佢呢家有冇變？"},"citedBy":0,"rep